This petition has the objective of democratically compelling the government of the UK to use its best (lawful) endeavours, including economic sanctions and international diplomacy, to secure the following:

(1) The immediate cessation of military action by Israel in Palestine;

(2) The immediate abandonment by Israel of the policy of expansion into Palestinian land on the basis of theological entitlement or any other basis not in step with international norms;

(3) For both parties to the conflict to consent to a neutral UN peacekeeping force to go on the ground in Palestine with a mandate to enforce the peace and protect civilians. Such a mandate to include authorisation for proportionate force to prevent the utilisation of rocket attacks from within Palestinian land.
